্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/024_062_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55613,"position":38,"arabic":"غَفُورٌۭ","translation":"ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/024_062_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55614,"position":39,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"পরম দয়ালু","audioUrl":"wbw/024_062_042.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55615,"position":40,"arabic":"٦٢","translation":"(৬২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":63,"arabic":"لَّا تَجْعَلُوا۟ دُعَآءَ ٱلرَّسُولِ بَيْنَكُمْ كَدُعَآءِ بَعْضِكُم بَعْضًۭا ۚ قَدْ يَعْلَمُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلَّذِينَ يَتَسَلَّلُونَ مِنكُمْ لِوَاذًۭا ۚ فَلْيَحْذَرِ ٱلَّذِينَ يُخَالِفُونَ عَنْ أَمْرِهِۦٓ أَن تُصِيبَهُمْ فِتْنَةٌ أَوْ يُصِيبَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ","translation":"DO NOT regard the Apostles summons to you [in the same light] as a summons of one of you to another: God is indeed aware of those of you who would withdraw surreptitiously: so let those who would go against His bidding beware, lest a [bitter] trial befall them [in this world] or grievous suffering befall them [in the life to come].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2854.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":56116,"position":1,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56117,"position":2,"arabic":"تَجْعَلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা গণ্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56118,"position":3,"arabic":"دُعَآءَ","translation":"আহ্বানকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56119,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولِ","translation":"রাসূলের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56120,"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56121,"position":6,"arabic":"كَدُعَآءِ","translation":"আহ্বানের মতো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_063_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56122,"position":7,"arabic":"بَعْضِكُم","translation":"তোমাদের একে","audioUrl"